# Running System Tests with Security Enabled


The objective of running system tests with Security(Auth+TLS) enabled is to very that all Pravega functionality continues to function the same way as expected in an environment where auth is disabled.
This also aims to cover testing of a few security specific test scenarios, as listed here,but will not cover each and every test path for Pravega Security testing. This should be covered by Security Unit Tests.

The following approaches have been considered for running System Tests with & without Security:
